OL,4,Cblame if Liverpool do not win title
OL,6,FMerseyside derby referee Michael
OL,7,FOliver has claimed Liverpool head
OL,8,Fcoach Arne Slot told him he would be
OL,9,Fto blame if his side did not win the
OL,10,Fleague.
OL,12,FOliver's claims that Slot and his
OL,13,Fassistant Sipke Hulshoff made abusive
OL,14,Fcomments towards him were detailed in
OL,15,Fa copy of his match report that was
OL,16,Fpresented to an independent regulatory
OL,17,Fcommission.
