OL,6,FSlot and Hulshoff were both shown red
OL,7,Fcards after confronting Oliver on the
OL,8,Fpitch after James Tarkowski scored an
OL,9,Fequaliser for Everton in the eighth
OL,10,Fminute of added time.
OL,12,FThe 2-2 draw in February 2025, which
OL,13,Falso saw Curtis Jones and Everton's
OL,14,FAbdoulaye Doucoure sent off for
OL,15,Fscuffling after the final whistle,
OL,16,Fmeant the Reds missed the chance to
OL,17,Fmove nine points clear at the top of
OL,18,Fthe table.
