OL,3,CReferee claims Arne Slot said he is to
OL,4,Cblame if Liverpool do not win title
OL,6,FIn Oliver's match report he alleged a
OL,7,F"confrontational and aggressive" Slot
OL,8,Fhad told the official he had "f***king
OL,9,Fgive them everything" and he hoped he
OL,10,F"was proud of that performance".
OL,12,FOliver then claimed Slot returned to
OL,13,Fadd "if we don't win the league, I'll
OL,14,Ff***ing blame you", before telling an
OL,15,Fassistant referee it was "a f***ing
OL,16,Fdisgrace".
OL,18,FOliver said Hulshoff alleged he said
OL,19,Fhe was "f***ing sh*t" and "gave them
OL,20,Feverything" and he was a "f***ing
OL,21,Fdisgrace".
