OL,6,FSlot admitted the charges but insisted
OL,7,Fhe said "if we don't win the league, I
OL,8,Fwill have you to thank for that".
OL,10,FHowever, the FA maintained Slot's
OL,11,Flanguage and words were as reported by
OL,12,FOliver and that the discrepancy did
OL,13,Fnot make a material difference to the
OL,14,Fsanction.
OL,16,FSlot and Hulshoff were subsequently
OL,17,Fgiven two-match touchline suspensions
OL,18,Fand fined for their behaviour.
