OL,6,FIn its written reasons, the commission
OL,7,Fsaid their cases were viewed as "non-
OL,8,Fstandard" because the Football
OL,9,FAssociation considered the misconduct
OL,10,Fto be of a serious and/or unusual
OL,11,Fnature.
OL,13,FSlot acknowledged his actions were
OL,14,Funacceptable and allowed frustration
OL,15,Fto get the better of him as he
OL,16,Fbelieved certain key decisions did not
OL,17,Fgo Liverpool's way, and it was noted
OL,18,Fhe made sincere apologies both in
OL,19,Fprivate and public.
