OL,3,CReferee claims Arne Slot said he is to
OL,4,Cblame if Liverpool do not win title
OL,6,FThe commission said: "Arne Slot, as
OL,7,Fthe manager of LFC, is a role model
OL,8,Fand should be exercising good
OL,9,Fdiscipline both on and off the pitch,
OL,10,Fand setting an example to his players"
OL,11,Fand his actions "did not provide the
OL,12,Fpositive image of the game that the
OL,13,Fgoverning bodies strive for."
OL,15,FIt did, however, state were it not for
OL,16,Fthe mitigating circumstances of both
OL,17,Fmen's previous good records a three-
OL,18,Fmatch ban would have been imposed `
OL,19,Fwhich would have meant the pair
OL,20,Fmissing this month's Carabao Cup final.
